Franciscus Name Popularity

At NamesLook, the name Franciscus is recorded 168 times globally, ranking it as the 130,212th most common name worldwide.

Franciscus is most prevalent in Netherlands, with 77 occurrences, making it the 5,386th most popular name in the country.
